postcontent: Used Ruger 10/22 in an ATI Scorpion 6 position, side folding stock.  Comes with original stock, original 10 round magazine, a Ruger double BX25 magazine, and a Sightmark Mini shot red dot sight mounted on a picitiny rail I mounted to the receiver.  Works great.  Only reason for selling it is after I bought a 22lr conversion kit for my AR 15 it just sits in the safe.  Not selling for any other reason so please dont send low ball offers.
